                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The  total  errors  of  the  reduced cross",
                " sections  as  calculated   by   the   analysis   are",
                " presented."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The corrections were made for  the  response  of  the",
                " beam monitor to the bremsstrahlung beam."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Measurements of  the  (g,np) cross sections of Ge-70,",
                " Ge-72,  Ge-74,  and Ge-76 and (g,p) cross section of",
                " Ge-74 are reported. The (g,np) reaction is discussed",
                " as a channel for the observation of the T = T0  +  1",
                " component  of  the  giant  dipole  resonance  of the",
                " nuclear photoeffect,  and experimental  evidence  is",
                " presented  in  support  of  this  conjecture  in  Ge",
                " isotopes."
              ]
            }
          ],
